Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.00,0:01:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前方300公尺處的建築物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.64,0:01:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的七樓就是目的地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.20,0:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.68,0:01:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.35,0:01:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.25,0:02:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.32,0:02:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.82,0:02:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.85,0:02:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.72,0:02:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑到哪裡去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.39,0:02:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#08         ちぃ，困惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.02,0:03:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.89,0:03:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳跑到哪裡去了？ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.43,0:03:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回簽我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑到哪裡去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.29,0:03:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡 發生了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.10,0:03:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬，用四分之一倍速重播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.50,0:03:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.32,0:04:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.22,0:04:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.83,0:04:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能再打一次電話給稔他們嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，絲茉茉，妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.80,0:04:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉，絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.54,0:04:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是壞了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.71,0:04:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.94,0:04:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死，她可是借來的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.41,0:04:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.95,0:04:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是北口派出所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.52,0:04:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將電腦停在站前廣場的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.99,0:04:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請儘速搬離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.96,0:04:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重複一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.53,0:04:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是北口派出所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.73,0:04:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將電腦停在站前廣場的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.07,0:04:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請儘速搬離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.77,0:04:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會妨礙到交通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請儘速搬離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，我們的能動嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.81,0:05:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連原因都不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.31,0:05:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.21,0:05:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.68,0:05:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全無法重新開機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.82,0:05:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.76,0:05:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.86,0:05:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.39,0:05:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣都動不了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.63,0:05:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道為什麼會變成這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.16,0:05:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是望了一下\N站在時鐘上的那台電腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就突然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.70,0:05:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時鐘？電腦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.88,0:05:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.81,0:05:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都沒看到你說的那種東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.38,0:05:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑到哪裡去了？ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.39,0:06:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.93,0:06:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.93,0:06:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳聽不見嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.19,0:06:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.86,0:07:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.34,0:07:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問… 發生什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.68,0:07:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才想問妳 發生什麼事了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.81,0:07:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.61,0:07:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.25,0:07:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.55,0:07:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.42,0:08:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，得想辦法帶她回去才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1，2，3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.36,0:08:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.93,0:08:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今，逼不得已了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生，那女孩是電腦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在外面當機了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.11,0:08:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然電腦很方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.21,0:08:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來反而讓你多花了一筆錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.68,0:08:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.88,0:08:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過ちぃ對我而言\N是非常重要的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.79,0:08:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.88,0:09:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像做了一個\N如同動作片電影般的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.58,0:09:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過昨晚還真嚇人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明 發生了那種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還睡得這麼熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.63,0:09:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.43,0:09:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看起來好像是睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.83,0:09:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但實際上她並不是在睡覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.70,0:09:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚她就不曾睜開眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.11,0:09:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會就這樣不動了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.44,0:09:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.48,0:09:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不動了，那該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.58,0:09:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.32,0:09:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果一直都是這樣的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.19,0:09:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒啊，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.70,0:09:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.83,0:09:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，秀樹，秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.30,0:09:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您還要再喝一杯嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，麻煩妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.97,0:10:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.30,0:10:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保有寄郵件過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.97,0:10:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說費了很大的功夫才找到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.44,0:10:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經把她帶回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.21,0:10:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.72,0:10:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.28,0:10:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這附近的電腦都當機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.79,0:10:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬妳也不清楚原因對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.23,0:10:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於當時的狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.17,0:11:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.57,0:11:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有聽到什麼聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.44,0:11:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰的聲音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.01,0:11:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.32,0:11:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.89,0:11:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是某位我認識的人的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.66,0:11:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.70,0:11:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.77,0:11:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？妳再給我說一次看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.30,0:11:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ昨天去打工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.27,0:11:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是跟妳說不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.64,0:11:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以去做有問題的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.45,0:11:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，秀樹有說過不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.68,0:11:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以ちぃ沒做有問題的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.79,0:11:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷窺小屋就是有問題的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.66,0:11:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.09,0:12:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個哥哥說是好工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.23,0:12:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種人一定會那麼說的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.13,0:12:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹說ちぃ去打工的話\N秀樹會高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.97,0:12:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹說想拿錢去買各種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.31,0:12:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說了讓她產生誤解的話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.25,0:12:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ做錯了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.09,0:12:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ不乖嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.75,0:12:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.42,0:12:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ一點都沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.13,0:12:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.23,0:12:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.93,0:12:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ沒做錯事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.01,0:12:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ不想讓秀樹討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.78,0:12:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為秀樹是ちぃ的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興妳有這份心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.95,0:13:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ不用勉強去打工也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.32,0:13:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹說過會高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.66,0:13:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.36,0:13:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這樣做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.63,0:13:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幫妳去找工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在找到之前ちぃ要乖乖看家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.00,0:13:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.00,0:13:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，謝謝秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.04,0:13:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.68,0:13:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要道謝的人應該是我才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.95,0:13:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.88,0:13:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.25,0:13:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.42,0:13:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡要注意的是用到\N“TAMAHE”這個詞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.86,0:13:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,條件是短期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.82,0:13:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又安全的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.46,0:13:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後又肯用不懂常識的ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.53,0:13:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有可能會有這種好地方嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.51,0:13:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請別在意昨天那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.81,0:14:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，不過我好想吃\N裕美親手煮的料理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.58,0:14:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還好電腦沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.02,0:14:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.95,0:14:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過她好像沒有就此氣餒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.92,0:14:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不幫她找到新工作的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.42,0:14:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她大概又會去做一些怪事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.66,0:14:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來只能靠我幫她找了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過也不會啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.93,0:14:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比想像的還要容易就找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.24,0:14:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家電腦的打工地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.50,0:14:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看，這條商店街不是有間叫\N“奇洛如”的糕餅店嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.44,0:14:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡好像在舉辦什麼慶祝活動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.21,0:14:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五週年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.15,0:14:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.55,0:14:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是開幕五週年的慶祝活動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.49,0:14:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廣告單上是這麼寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.49,0:14:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，就是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.19,0:14:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後我去跟店長談了以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.49,0:14:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說願意雇用ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.73,0:14:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.23,0:14:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼順利的就找到打工的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.97,0:14:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.34,0:15:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，開店了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.14,0:15:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意之至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.54,0:15:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，裕美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.85,0:15:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在舉辦\N奇洛如開幕五週年慶祝活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.76,0:15:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要購買糕點就送您精美禮品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.30,0:15:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在舉辦\N奇洛如開幕五週年慶祝活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.60,0:15:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要購買糕點就送您…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.07,0:15:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.51,0:15:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.28,0:15:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那電腦做得好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.18,0:15:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好像是電腦耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.11,0:15:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看那對耳朵就知道了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.49,0:15:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是電腦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.49,0:15:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.49,0:15:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.09,0:15:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這段從“伊勢物語”節錄出的\N例句中的“SABURAI”一詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.83,0:16:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與竹取物語“節錄出的\N例句中的”SABURAI
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.03,0:16:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當句尾銜接“TE”或“KEMU”時…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.40,0:16:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有沒有好好的在做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有給人添麻煩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.37,0:16:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.44,0:16:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.78,0:16:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下班時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.22,0:16:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天妳可以收工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.52,0:16:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收工？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.39,0:16:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是今天工作就到此結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.72,0:16:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ是第一次打工所以不太懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.46,0:16:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ有做錯事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.83,0:16:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒有做錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.90,0:16:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ很努力工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.24,0:16:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在幫了我很大的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，拿得到錢嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.24,0:16:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.48,0:16:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，裡面是今天的薪水\N（本須和ちぃ小姐）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.58,0:16:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是錢嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.62,0:16:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是信封
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.59,0:16:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢在那裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.79,0:17:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面的東西能買東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.53,0:17:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.76,0:17:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹想要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.73,0:17:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能用這裡面的東西買到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.40,0:17:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ很多事都不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.20,0:17:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想學習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.24,0:17:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,植田弘康店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.37,0:17:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請教我各種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.94,0:17:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…不用叫我的全名啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.05,0:17:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我店長就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.21,0:17:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.28,0:17:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.38,0:17:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人叫店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.09,0:17:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.86,0:17:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.92,0:17:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳果真如同本須和所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.89,0:17:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不太懂一般常識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.73,0:17:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還好是個好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.30,0:17:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ是好孩子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.40,0:17:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同本須和所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個很好的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.57,0:17:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ是好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.39,0:18:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，今天辛苦妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.36,0:18:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ回去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只剩下店長一個人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.26,0:18:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有其他打工的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.97,0:18:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實，以前有請過一個女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.70,0:18:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.51,0:18:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.21,0:18:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.04,0:18:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.68,0:18:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,週年慶結束後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.61,0:18:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還願意來奇洛如打工嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,週年慶結束後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.82,0:18:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還願意來奇洛如打工…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.22,0:18:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳願意的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.53,0:18:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回去問秀樹行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.20,0:18:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，如果本須和同意的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.70,0:18:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每週都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.40,0:18:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長，你沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.67,0:18:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是沒事，但不行這麼做喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不行？打工嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.11,0:19:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不能隨便擁抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.88,0:19:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能擁抱嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.82,0:19:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這要看對方是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.19,0:19:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的人才可以呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.42,0:19:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.49,0:19:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,例如ちぃ喜歡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.43,0:19:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ喜歡的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.87,0:19:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果只屬於我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.24,0:19:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得只喜歡我一個人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.84,0:19:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是只屬於我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.62,0:19:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.88,0:19:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.42,0:19:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.52,0:19:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看，他來接妳了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.42,0:19:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ 發了糕點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.49,0:19:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長叫作店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇洛如是糕餅店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.60,0:19:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長是植田弘康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.47,0:19:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過他叫店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長比秀樹還高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.34,0:20:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長要我以後也繼續來工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.34,0:20:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.47,0:20:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以秀樹，秀樹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.94,0:20:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦，講慢一點，好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.68,0:20:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.45,0:20:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要妳繼續去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.99,0:20:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.99,0:20:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.89,0:20:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.12,0:20:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.12,0:20:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ能繼續打工嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.58,0:20:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.28,0:20:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.51,0:20:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用那個能買到\N秀樹喜歡的東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.78,0:20:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是ちぃ的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.63,0:21:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.84,0:21:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是ちぃ賺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.70,0:21:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以是ちぃ的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.51,0:21:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹不想要錢嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.21,0:21:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是不想要，不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.78,0:21:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.82,0:21:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有這份心 我就很高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.65,0:21:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.65,0:21:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.02,0:21:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿這個去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.59,0:21:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能買到跟這些錢等值的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.70,0:21:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去買妳喜歡的東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.07,0:21:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是ちぃ覺得想要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.37,0:21:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.21,0:21:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能擁抱你嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.58,0:21:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳怎麼了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼嚴肅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.81,0:21:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.12,0:21:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.68,0:22:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的走在熟悉的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.82,0:22:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確會照映在眼簾中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.67,0:22:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在成群結隊前進的人群中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.77,0:22:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那顆遭到淹沒         感到膽怯的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.61,0:22:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raison         d'etre         像那種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.28,0:23:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raison         d'etre         如同那般的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.62,0:23:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡笑、沉沒、漂流\N究竟是為了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.49,0:23:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找著那把鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.37,0:23:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷的在尋找著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.54,0:23:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.77,0:23:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那扇門的鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.23,0:23:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.83,0:23:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在要教妳澡堂的鐵則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.56,0:23:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.16,0:23:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.66,0:23:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.33,0:23:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,付洗澡錢一定要用銅板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.00,0:23:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.57,0:23:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.17,0:23:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以在腰部圍毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.23,0:23:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.73,0:23:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.50,0:23:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論水多熱都不能加冷水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.04,0:23:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.60,0:23:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.17,0:23:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在浴池泡澡時要將毛巾放在頭上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.04,0:23:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.01,0:23:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.64,0:23:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗完澡喝牛奶時要將手叉在腰上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.98,0:24:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.28,0:24:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.32,0:24:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits         下一回\N「ちぃ，購物」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.08,0:24:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附註一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.79,0:24:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果汁牛奶只能在\N有好事 發生的日子才能喝
